{"tid":1633072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要]示威區有好多人需要幫忙，請大家幫好幫滿","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:40:01.000Z","uid":97181,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b176d6f82782f07bf8d6128d75f5a3a04849c58","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:15:12.000Z","msg":"各位都明白佔咗路，車就行唔到<br />\n偏偏各個示威區都好多酒店<br />\n遊客或者公幹人士帶住好多行李<br />\n好需要有車運行李到酒店門口<br />\n<br />\n話說尋日兩點幾我係太古廣場三期<br />\n見到一位身形嬌小的日本女士<br />\n嘗試推住隻30吋喼加巨型行李袋上星街<br />\n咁啱落緊大雨，佢推唔夠20米上半身已經濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開口一問，原來佢係要去JW Marriott<br />\n人生路不熟夠慘，加上落住雨推住隻大喼，不特只仲要上錯斜路，我估佢當時一定懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二話不說立刻指返條正確的路先<br />\n不過見到佢個表情就知道，聽到又要上斜仲慘過返日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果我叫佢幫我擔遮，我幫佢經正義道推到去JW Marriott門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後佢唔知點報答，想攞錢出黎塞比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我當然無要到啦，咁先體現到香港好客之道架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知道佢有無share返呢件事比朋友知<br />\n但我知道抗爭時間，有啲嘢唔係有鏡頭先做。記住我地係要體現香港民族的勇氣同優秀，唔係成為人見人怕的魔鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共勉之<br />\n<br />\nBTW，載日本女士個的士司機反省吓自己，PP3門口放低人之後，竟然亂指條路叫人上星街，萬一女士淋雨病咗，或者被個喼搞到受傷，你良心過唔過意得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef125ad118263791844499f87e645ab72b5def1","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77a3cd4846a56182d02a09d42b29acc3c26fa8f2","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:18:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0e609f7063477633c720b8a756fd0c97b77d248","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:18:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13f6f99c0e495b74d79241a93cd9dde24a048ec5","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"314f3a1f2ef08a8492864bc0d201fc81c16715f8","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afc9e29b4533be6b59658d361dd022e60ffa1477","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aad1cd27d51a1c5845c4bd8c1a287f177e9faa12","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8acdba1af75238cb87e552265f7f2d22812a2fe1","tid":1633072,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:31:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"87717cf2669b38f436e51bb1b5fa3a33d354b396","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:33:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f97bdc5b540b2a8ff51c68654f35ca5cf34db878","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4ca56655975a21f38b0fe9d743f96315d929429","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ea9739b3976fc3fe922b82ad0a045b26773f6d5","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8b60de92c2e73689c5b072d7bc7321938d77925","tid":1633072,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abf075231771bf12aed288067f46cdd9f9afb80e","tid":1633072,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"【緊急！】【討論至達成共識！】今日開花三點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633396</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca12698d3a